social_posts.post_text: If only I’d known what this year would bring. 💫💫
So much to learn from my littlest babe. She leads the most simple, magical existence.🌹🌼🌺🌸🌷☀️🌈

My daughter Lily and I have created something truly magical - both in terms of our beautiful designs and the amazing purpose they serve. 

Every item purchased helps provide lifesaving treatments to an orphaned or abandoned baby at OVI Children’s Hospital in Kenya.

We’re setting a big goal - we hope to find our first thirty-one customers by my 31st birthday this Sunday, March 26th. 

We’d be so grateful if you could help us make this wish come true by sharing this reel with your followers on social media.

DM me a screenshot of any purchases you make so we can celebrate together! 🎊 Cheers to the little actions that make the biggest difference! We are in urgent need of volunteers, sponsors, and advocates for our OVI Children’s Hospital in Migori, Kenya. Please send a DM saying “OVI” if you are interested in joining our mission at any capacity. Your support means absolutely everything to us. 🙏🏻
My entire soul leaps watching sweet Lily in her full courage and confidence. Thank you beautiful @ruthykimanimbugua & @villarosakempinski for creating the most magical experience for us. 💫💫

Every child deserves a chance at a healthy and happy life, and at OVI Children's Hospital, we're dedicated to making that a reality. As we approach this year's Giving Tuesday, we invite you to join us in our mission to create "A World Where No Child is Alone."

About Us:

OVI Children's Hospital has been providing free, life-saving treatment and holistic care to children in need since December 2017. Our approach goes beyond physical health, encompassing counseling, education, and support for children and families. We fight for every child, no matter their condition or life expectancy, and we work tirelessly to reunite children with loving families whenever possible.

Your Impact:

Your generosity on Giving Tuesday can make a profound difference in the lives of vulnerable children. Your donation will enable us to continue providing critical healthcare, emotional support, and transformative care. Together, we can prevent children from becoming institutionalized orphans and ensure that no child feels alone.

How You Can Help:

On Giving Tuesday, consider making a gift to OVI Children's Hospital. Your donation will go directly towards:

- Life-saving Treatment: Providing free, 24/7 hospital care to vulnerable children.
- Holistic Services: Offering counseling, education, and support for emotional well-being.
- Family Reunification: Reuniting children with loving families and preventing abandonment.
- Preventing Orphanhood: Supporting vulnerable mothers and children to keep families together.

Thank you for being a part of our journey. Your generosity brings smiles to the faces of children who need it most.

Together, we can change lives. Together, we can create a world where no child is alone.

#GivingTuesday #TransformingLives #OVIChildrensHospital

🌟 Friends, this Giving Tuesday, I'm reaching out with a heartfelt ask. 🌟

Will you join me in providing hope to orphaned, abandoned, and at-risk children? For just $35 a month, you can help our OVI Children's Hospital offer them essential 24/7 hospital care free of charge.

As a token of gratitude, each new monthly donor will receive a handcrafted ornament and a heartfelt photo of one of the children your gift is supporting.

Let's be the change-makers these children need.

www.OVIHealthcare.org/give 

Together, we can create a world where every child receives the care they deserve. 💕
